{"tid":21370,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"想享受Hall Life 唔好揀理工","createTime":"2016-12-03T19:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T08:36:54.000Z","uid":54201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6ed6fb51573145ff97c9b24968e16d3d0a1ccdb","tid":21370,"uid":54201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T19:35:05.000Z","msg":"理工宿舍同監獄冇咩大分別相信好多人都知<br />\n<br />\n由嚴厲打擊男女同房（12:00-07:00不得踏入異性房間，違者永久不能申請住宿舍，7年不得進入宿舍範圍，兼且所有已付宿費不獲退回）<br />\n<br />\n至早前差一步就實施既訪客條例（每次只能帶同最多3位朋友，每月最多帶4次朋友進入宿舍）<br />\n<br />\n仲有早前實施過一排既濕鳩條例（訪客進入宿舍範圍時，宿生不得離開宿舍）<br />\n<br />\n到今日，岩岩被逼裝既國產路由器，令到原本上網慢到有時連YouTube 1080p都睇唔到既速度，變成5分鐘斷一次線，Facebook load 240p既片都會疾下疾下。除此之外，仲要block左D AV網站。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母唔比人扑野都算，飛機都唔撚比打。我究竟做錯咩事揀左poly，上網睇下電影都唔撚比<br />\n<br />\n我宣布理工大學係咁多間大學染得最紅既一間，連上網都要翻牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ffe12cc3fddd568b56af5ca38e7b6b397bd6511","tid":21370,"uid":34621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T19:36:22.000Z","msg":"新hall<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4b81802b1eb6bb4240c151ded459555bfdc079","tid":21370,"uid":54201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T19:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新hall<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n緊係舊hall<br />\n<br />\n新hall一早比蝗蟲一帶一路佔領左"},{"pid":"6fc89755d28a5c24e2c0916cde3aaa0a833e66cb","tid":21370,"uid":54201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾poly"},{"pid":"7263ba05910b0017807b62b433b42607df8ac034","tid":21370,"uid":47926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:36:54.000Z","msg":"裝完無幾耐今日完全上唔到網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係右邊裝番自己個router喇巴打<br />\nBtw更正番之前果個政策一個月訪客最多只可以入5次 垃圾紅監"}]}